hadiths[65]{hadithnumber,text}:
5575,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jisne duniya mein sharab pi aur phir us ne tauba nahi ki to aakhirat mein wo us se mahroom rahega.
5576,"jis raat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko meraaj karaai gaee to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko) baitul-maqdis ke Shahar ( iiliyaa mein sharab aur doodh ke 2 pyaley pesh kiye gaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein dekha phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne doodh ka piyala ley liya. is par Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne kaha us Allah ke liye tamam ta'reefein hain jisne aapko Deen fitrat ki taraf chalney ki hidayat farmai . agar aap ne sharab ka piyala ley liya hota to aap ki ummat gumrah ho jati. Shuaib ke sath us hadis ko Mamar , ibnul-haad, Usman bin umr aur Zubaidi ne Zohri se naql kya hai."
5577,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aik hadis suni jo tum se ab mere siwa koi aur nahi bayan karega (kyonke ab mere siwa koi sahabi zinda maujood nahi raha hai). Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke qiyamat ki nishaniyon mein se ye hai ke jahaalat ghalib ho jaeygi aur ilm kam ho jaeyga zinaakaarii badh jaeygi, sharab kasarat se pi janey lagegii, auratein bahut ho jaaeingii, yahan tak ke pachaas-pachaas aurton ki nigrani karne wala sirf aik hi mard reh jaeyga"
5578,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke koi shakhs jab zina karta hai to theek zina kartey waqt wo momin nahi hota. isi tarah jab wo sharab peetaa hai to theek sharab peetey waqt wo momin nahi hota. isi tarah jab chor chori karta hai to us waqt wo momin nahi hota aur ibne-Shahab ne bayan kya, unhein Abdul-Malik -bin-abi-Bakr bin Abdur-Rehman bin Haris-bin-Hisham ne khabar di, unse Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey they aur unse Abu-Hurera (rz). phir unhon-ne bayan kya ke Abu-Bakar bin Abdur-Rehman Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadis mein zikr kiye huey maamlon ke sath itna aur zyada kartey they ke koi shakhs (din dahaadey) agar kisi badi poonjii par is tarah daaka daalta hai ke log dekhtey ke dekhtey reh jatey hain to wo momin rahtey huey ye loot-maar nahi karta."
5579,jab sharab haram ki gaee to angoor ki sharab Madina Munawra mein nahi miltii thi.
5580,"ham se Yunus ne, unse Sabit Bunani ne aur unse Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke jab sharab ham par haram ki gaee to Madina Munawra mein angoor ki sharab bahut kam miltii thi. aam istemal ki sharab kachchi aur pakkii khajoor se taiyaar ki jati thi."
5581,"ham se Aamir ne bayan kya aur unse ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) mimber par khadey huey aur kaha ammaa ba'd! jab sharab ki hurmat ka hukm nazil hua to wo panch chizon se bantii thi angoor, khajoor, shahad, gehun aur jau aur sharab (khamr) wo hai jo aql ko mitaa de."
5582,"mein abu-Ubaida, abu-Talha aur Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ko kachchi aur pakkii khajoor se taiyaar ki hui sharab pilaa raha tha ke aik aaney waley ne aa kar bataya ke sharab haram kar di gaee hai. us waqt abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Anas utho aur sharab ko baha do chunanche maine usey baha diya."
5583,"aik qabeele mein khada main apne chachaon ko khajoor ki sharab pilaa raha tha main unmein sabse kam Umr tha. kisi ne kaha ke sharab haram kar di gaee. un hazraat ne kaha ke ab usey phenk do. chunanche ham ne sharab phenk di. maine Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke wo kis cheez ki sharab bantii thi? farmaya ke taaza pakkii hui aur kachchi khajooron ki. Abu-Bakar bin Anas ne kaha ke unki sharab ( khajoor ki) hoti thi to Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne iska inkar nahi kya aur mujh se mere kuchh ashaab ne bayan kya ke unhon-ne Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne bayan kya ke us zamane mein unki sharab aksar kachchi aur pakkii khajoor se taiyaar ki jati thi."
5584,mujh se Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke jab sharab haram ki gaee to wo kachchi aur pukhta khajooron se taiyaar ki jati thi.
5585,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se (bitaa') ke mutaalliq puchha gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo bhi peeney wali cheez nasha laavey wo haram hai.
5586,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ( bitaa' (ke mutaalliq sawal kya gaya. ye mashroob shehad se taiyaar kya jata tha aur Yaman mein iska aam riwaaj tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo cheez bhi nasha laney wali ho wo haram hai.
5587,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ''dabbaa''aur ''muzaffat'' mein nabeez na banaya karo aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) iske sath '' hantam ''aur '' naqeer '' ka bhi izafa kya kartey they.
5588,"umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke member par khutba detey huey kaha jab sharab ki hurmat ka hukm hua to wo panch chizon se bantii thi. angoor se, khajoor se, gehun se, jau aur shehad se aur (khamr) wo hai jo aql nasha taarii kar de aur teen masayel aisey hain ke meri tamanna thi ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ham se juda honey se pahley hamein unka hukm bata jatey, dada ka mas'ala, kalaala ka masla aur sood ke chand masaayel. abu-Hayyan ne bayan kya ke maine Shabi se puchha : aey abu-Amr ! aik aisa sharbat hai jo sindh mein chaawal se banaya jata hai. unhon-ne kaha ke ye cheez Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein nahi paai jati thi ya kaha ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke zamaney mein na thi aur farj ibne-minhaal ne bhi is hadis ko Hammaad-bin-Salma se bayan kya aur unse abu-Hayyan ne usmein angoor ke bajaey kishmish hai."
5589,"umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke sharab panch chizon se bantii thi kishmish , khajoor , geihun, jau aur shehad se."
5590,"mujh se abu-Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ya abu-Malik Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya : Allah ki qism ! unhon-ne jhoot nahi bayan kya ke unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke meri ummat mein aisey burey log paida ho jaeinge jo zinaakaarii karenge, resham pehna karenge, sharab piyaa karenge aur gaaney bajaey ko halal bana lengey aur kuchh mutakabbir qism ke log pahaad ki choti par (apne banglon mein rihaaish karne ke liye) chaley jaengey. charwaahey unke maweshii subah w Sham laaengey aur ley jaengey. unke paas aik faqeer aadmi apni zarurat lekar jaeyga to wo taalney ke liye us se kahengey ke kal aana lekin Allah Taala raat ko unko (unki sarkashi ki wjah se) halaak kar dega pahaad ko (un par) gira dega aur unmein se bahut son ko qiyamat tak ke liye bandar aur Sura ki Suraton mein maskh kar dega."
5591,"abu-Usaid Malik bin Rabe aaey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko apne waleeme ki dawat di, unki biwi hi sab kaam kar rahi thin halanke wo nai dulhan thin. Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya tumhen malum hai ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko kya pilaya tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye unhon-ne patthar ke koondey mein raat ke waqt khajoor bhigo di thi."
5592,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chand bartanon mein nabeez bhigoney ki (jin mein sharab bantii thi) manaahii kar di thi phir Ansar ne arz kya ke hamarey paas to doosrey bartan nahi hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke to khair phir ijazat hai. imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) kehtey hain mujh se khaleefa bin khayyaat ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Yahya-bin-Saeed qattaan ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Sufiyan Sory ne bayan kya, unse Mansoor bin Motamir ne aur unse Saalim-bin abi-Jad ne phir yahi hadis riwayat ki thi."
5593,"jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mashkon ke siwa aur bartanon mein nabeez bhigoney se mana farmaya to logon ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! har kisi ko mashk kahan se mil sakti hai? us waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bin laakh lagey ghadey ( raughane-zuft lagey bartan ( mein nabeez bhigoney ki ijazat de di. ham se Abdullah-bin Muhammad masnadii ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Sufiyan Sory ne yahi bayan kya aur is mein yun hai ke jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chand bartanon mein nabeez bhigoney se mana farmaayaa."
5594,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dabbaa aur muzaffat ( khas qism ke bartan jin mein sharab bantii thi) ke istemal ki bhi manaahii kar di thi. ham se Usman ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Jarir ne bayan kya, kaha unse Aamash ne yahi hadis bayan ki."
5595,"maine Aswad bin Yazeed se puchha kya tum ne Ummul-Momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se puchha tha ke kis bartan mein nabeez (khajoor ka meethaa sharbat) banaanaa makruh hai? unhon-ne kaha ke ji haan, maine arz kya ummul-momeneen! kis bartan mein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne nabeez banaaney se mana farmaya tha. unhon-ne kaha ke khas ghar walon ko kadu ki tonbii aur laakhii bartan mein nabeez bhigoney se mana farmaya tha. (Ibraaheem Nakhai ne bayan kya ke) maine Aswad se puchha unhon-ne ghadey aur sabz martban ka zikr nahi kya. usne kaha ke main tum se wahi bayan karta hun jo maine suna, kya wo bhi bayan kar dun jo maine na suna ho?"
5596,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sabz ghadey se mana farmaya tha, maine puchha kya ham safaid ghadon mein pi liya karein kaha ke nahi."
5597,"abu-Usaid Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne waleeme ki dawat Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko di, us din unki biwi (umme-Usaid Sulaamaa) hi mahmaanon ki khidmat kar rahi thin. bevi abu-Usaid ne kaha tum jantey ho maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye kis cheez ka sharbat taiyaar kya tha patthar ke koondey mein raat ke waqt kuchh khajoorein bhigo di thin aur doosrey din subah ko aapko pilaa di thi."
5598,maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se ( باذق ( ) angoor ka sheera halki aanch diya hua) ke mutaalliq puchha to unhon-ne kaha ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( باذق (ke wujood se pahley hi duniya se rukhsat ho gaey they jo cheez bhi nasha laey wo haram hai. abul-Juweriya ne kaha ke) باذق ( to halal w paak hai. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke angoor halal w paak tha jab uski sharab bin gaee to wo haram khabees hai (na ke halal w paak) .
5599,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) halwaa aur shehad ko dost rakhtey they.
5600,"maine abu-Talha, abu-Dujaana aur Suhel bin baizaa (Raziallahu anhu) ko kachchi khajoor ki mili hui nabeez pilaa raha tha ke sharab haram kar di gaee aur maine maujooda sharab phenk di. main hi unhein pilaa raha tha main sabse kam Umr tha. ham us nabeez ko us waqt sharab hi samajhtey they aur Amr-bin-Haris rawi ne bayan kya ke ham se Qatada ne bayan kya, unhon-ne Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna."
5601,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kishmish aur khajoor (ke sheere) ko aur taaza (pukhta, pakkii hui) khajoor aur neem pukhta (kachchii, gadrii hui) khajoor ko mila kar bhigoney se mana farmaya tha, us taur usmein nasha jaldi paida ho jata hai."
5602,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uski manaahii ki thi ke pukhta aur gadraaii hui khajoor, pukhta khajoor aur kishmish ko mila kar nabeez banaya jaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne har aik ko juda judaa bhigoney ka hukm diya."
5603,shabe-mea'raaj mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko doodh aur sharab ke 2 pyaley pesh kiye gaey.
5604,"Arfa ke din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke roza ke barey mein sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ko shuba tha. isliye maine aap ke liye aik bartan mein doodh bheja aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey pi liya. Humaidii kehtey hain kabhi Sufiyan is hadis ko yun bayan kartey they ke Arfa ke din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke roze ke barey mein logon ko shuba tha isliye umme-fazal ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye (doodh) bhejaa. kabhi Sufiyan us hadis ko mursalan Umme- Fazal se riwayat kartey they, Salim aur Umer ka naam na letey. jab unse poochhtey ke ye hadis mursal hai ya marfooan muttasil to wo us waqt kehtey (marfooa muttasil hai) umme-Fazal se marwi (bayan) hai (jo sahaabiya thiin)."
5605,abu Humaid Saaidi maqam naqeea' se doodh ka aik piyala (khulaa hua) laey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke usey dhak kar kyon nahi laey aik lakdi hi is par rakh letey.
5606,"unhon-ne bayan kya ke aik Ansari sahabi abu Humaid Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) maqam naqeea' se aik bartan mein doodh Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye laey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke usey dhak kar kyon nahi laaey, is par lakdi hi rakh detey aur Aamash ne kaha ke mujh se Abu-Sufiyan ne bayan kya, unse Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne aur unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yahi hadis bayan ki."
5607,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Makka Mukarrama se tashrif laey to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aap ke sath they Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke (raaste mein) ham aik charwaahey ke qareeb se guzrey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) piyaasey they phir maine aik pyaley main (charwaahey se poochh kar) kuchh doodh dohaa. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wo doodh piyaa aur us se mujhey khushi hasil hui aur suraaqa-bin-Ja'sham ghodey par Sawar hamarey paas ( ta'aqub kartey huey) pahunch gaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uske liye baddua ki. aakhir usne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) iske haq mein baddua na karein aur wo wapas ho jaeyga Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aisa hi kya.
5608,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kya hi umda sadqa hai khub doodh dene wali ontni jo kuchh dinon ke liye kisi ko Atiya ke taur par di gaee ho aur khub doodh dene wali bakri jo kuchh dinon ke liye Atiya ke taur par di gaee ho jis se subah w Sham doodh bartan bhar-bhar kar nikala jaey.
5609,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne doodh piyaa phir kulli ki aur farmaya ke ismein chiknaahat hoti hai.
5610,"unse Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab mujhey Sidratul-Muntahaa tak ley jaya gaya to wahan maine char nehrein dekhein . 2 zahiri nehrein aur 2 baatinii . zahiri nehrein to neel aur Furaat hain aur baatinii nehrein jannat ki 2 nehrein hain. phir mere paas teen pyaley laey gaey aik pyaley mein doodh tha, doosrey mein shehad tha aur teesrey mein sharab thi. maine wo piyala liya jis mein doodh tha aur piyaa . is par mujh se kaha gaya ke tum ne aur tumhari ummat ne asl fitrat ko pa liya. Hisham , Saeed aur Hammam ne Qatada se, unhon-ne Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Malik bin Sasa (Raziallahu anhu) se ye hadis riwayat ki hai. usmein nadiyon ka zikr to aisa hi hai lekin teen piyaalon ka zikr nahi hai."
5611,"abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas Madina ke tamam Ansar mein sabse zyada khajoor ke baghaat they aur unka sabse pasandida maal beerhaa ka baagh tha. ye masjide-Nabawi ke samney hi tha aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wahan tashrif ley jatey they aur uska umda pani peetey they. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir jab aayat لن تنالوا البر حتى تنفقوا مما تحبون‏ ''tum hargiz neki nahi paogey jab tak wo maal na kharch karo jo tumhen azeez ho.'' nazil hui to abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) khadey huey aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah! Allah Taala farmata hai لن تنالوا البر حتى تنفقوا مما تحبون‏ ''tum hargiz neki ko nahi paogey jab tak wo maal na kharch karo jo tumhen azeez ho.'' aur mujhey apne maal mein sabse zyada azeez beerhaa ka baagh hai aur wo Allah Taala ke raaste mein sadqa hai, iska sawab aur ajr main Allah ke yahan paaney ki ummeed rakhta hon, isliye ya Rasulullah ! aap jahan usey munasib khayal farmaein kharch karein. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke khub ye bahut hi fayda bakhsh maal hai ya (iske bajaey aap ne) ( رايح ( ) ya ke sath farmaya ( . rawi hadis Abdullah ko usmein shak tha (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse mazeed farmaya ke) jo kuchh tu ney kaha hai maine sun liya mera khayal hai ke tum usey apne rishte-daaron ko de do. abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya ke aisa hi karunga ya Rasulullah! chunanche unhon-ne apne rishte daaron apne chacha ke ladkon mein usey taqseem kar diya aur Ismail aur Yahya-bin-Yahya ne ( رايح‏ (ka lafz naql kya hai."
5612,"unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko doodh peetey dekha aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke ghar tashrif laey they (bayaan kya ke) maine bakri ka doodh nikala aur is mein kuwein ka taaza pani mila kar (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko) pesh kya aap ne piyala lekar piyaa . aap ke baain taraf Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) they aur daain taraf aik dehati tha aap ne apna baqi doodh dehati ko diya aur farmaya ke pahley daain taraf se, haan daain taraf waley ka haq hai."
5613,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) qabila Ansar ke aik sahabi ke yahan tashrif le gaey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aap ke aik rafeeq (abu-Bakar (rz)) bhi they. unse Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar tumharey yahan usi raat ka baasii pani kisi mishkeezey mein rakha hua ho (to hamein pulaao) warna munh laga ke pani pi lengey. Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke wo sahib (jinke yahan aap tashrif liye gaey they) apne baagh mein pani de rahe they. bayan kya ke un sahib ne kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! mere paas raat ka baasii pani maujood hai, aap chhappar mein tashrif ley chalein. bayan kya ke phir wo un donon hazraat ko sath lekar gaey phir unhon-ne aik piyaale mein pani liya aur apni aik doodh dene wali bakri ka usmein doodh nikaalaa. bayan kya ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey piyaa, iske baad aap ke rafeeq Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ne piyaa."
5614,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sheerinii aur shehad ko dost rakhtey they.
5615,wo Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein masjid Kufa ke sehan mein hazir huey phir Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne khadey ho kar piyaa aur kaha ke kuchh log khadey ho kar pani peeney ko makruh samajhtey hain halanke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko is tarah kartey dekha hai jis tarah tum ne mujhey is waqt khadey ho kar pani peetey dekha hai.
5616,"unhon-ne Zohar ki Namaz padhi phir Kufa ki masjid ke sehan mein logon ki zarooraton ke liye baith gaey. us arse mein Asr ki Namaz ka waqt aa gaya phir unke paas pani laya gaya. unhon-ne pani piyaa aur apna chehra aur hath dhoey, unke sar aur paon (ke dhoney ka bhi) zikr kya. phir unhon-ne khadey ho kar wuzu ka bacha hua pani piyaa, iske baad kaha ke kuchh log khadey ho kar pani peeney ko bura samajhtey hain halanke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yoonhii kya tha jis tarah maine kya, wuzu ka pani khadey ho kar piyaa."
5617,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne zamzam ka pani khadey ho kar piyaa.
5618,"unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye doodh ka aik piyala bheja maidan Arafaat mein. wo Arfa ke din ki Sham (Syria) ka waqt tha aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (apni sawari par) sawar they, aap ne apne hath mein wo piyala liya aur usey pi liya. Malik ne abu-Nazar se '' apne oont par '' ke alfaz zyada kiye."
5619,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein pani mila hua doodh pesh kya gaya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke dahini taraf aik dehati tha aur baain taraf Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pi kar baqi dehati ko diya aur farmaya ke daain taraf se, to daain taraf se."
5620,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aik sharbat laya gaya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usmein se piyaa , aap ke daain taraf aik ladka betha hua tha aur baain taraf boodhey log ( Khalid-bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) jaisey baithey huey) they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bachchey se kaha kya tum mujhey ijazat doge ke main un (boodhey logon) ko (pahley) de dun. ladkey ne kaha : Allah ki qasam, ya Rasulullah ! aap ke jhootey mein se milney waley apne hisse ke maamle mein, main kisi par eisaar nahi karunga. rawi ne bayan kya ke is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ladkey ke hath mein piyala de diya."
5621,"ham se Yahya bin Saleh ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Fulaih bin Sulaiman ne bayan kya, unse Saeed bin-Haaris ne aur unse Jabir-bin-Abdullah Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke nabii Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) qabila Ansar ke aik sahabi ke yahan tashrif ley gaey. aanhazrat (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aap ke aik rafeeq ne unhein salam kya aur unhoney salam ka jawab diya. phir arz kya ke ya Rasulullah! mere maan-baap aap par nisaar hun ye badi garmi ka waqt hai wo apney baagh mein pani dey rahey they. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya agar tumharey paas mashk mein raat ka rakha hua pani hai (to wo pilaa do) warna ham munh laga kar pi lengey. wo sahib is waqt bhii baagh mein pani dey rahey they. unhoney arz kya ya Rasulullah! mere paas mashk mein raat ka rakha hua baasii pani hai phir wo chheid (jhaunpdii) mein gaey aur aik pyaley mein baasii pani pi liya phir apni aik doodh dene wali bakri ka doodh is mein nikaalaa. aanhazrat (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey piyaa phir wo dobara laey aur is martaba aanhazrat (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke rafeeq Hazrat siddeeqe-akbar (Raziallahu anhu) ne piyaa."
5622,"main khada hua apne qabeele mein apne chachaon ko khajoor ki sharab pilaa raha tha. main unmein se sabse chhota tha, itney mein kisi ne kaha ke sharab haram kar di gaee ( abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha ke sharab phenk do. chunanche ham ne phenk di. Sulaiman ne kaha ke maine Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha us waqt log kis cheez ki sharab peetey they kaha ke pakkii aur kachchi khajoor ki Abu-Bakar bin Anas ne kaha ke yahi unki sharab hoti thi Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne iska inkar nahi kya, bakr-bin-abdullaah Muzni ya Qatada ne kaha aur mujh se kuchh logon ne bayan kya ke unhon-ne Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne bayan kya ke '' unki un dinon yahi ( فضیح ( unki sharab thi. ''"
5623,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke raat ki jab shuruaat ho ya (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ( jab Sham ho to apne bachchon ko rok lo (aur ghar se bahar na nikalney do) kyonke us waqt shaitan phail jatey hain phir jab raat ki aik ghadi guzar jaey to unhein chhod do aur darwazey band kar lo aur us waqt Allah ka naam lo kyonke shaitan band darwazey ko nahi kholtaa aur Allah ka naam lekar apne mishkezon ka munh baandh do. Allah ka naam lekar apne bartanon ko dhak do, chahe kisi cheez ko chaudai mein rakh kar hi dhak sako aur apne charagh (soney se pahley) bujhaa diya karo."
5624,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum jab soney lago to charagh bujhaa do. darwazey band kar do, mashkon ke munh baandh do aur khaney peeney ke bartanon ko dhanp do. Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke mera khayal hai ke ye bhi kaha chahe lakdi hi ke zariey se dhak sako jo uski chaudai mein bismillaah keh kar rakh di jaey."
5625,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mashkon mein (ikhtinaas) se mana farmaya. mashk ka munh khol kar usmein munh laga kar pani peeney se rokaa.
5626,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna ke aap ne mashkon main (ikhtinaas) se mana farmaya hai. Abdullah ne bayan kya ke Mamar ne bayan kya ya unke ghair ne ke (ikhtinaas) mashk se munh laga kar pani peeney ko kehtey hain.
5627,"ham se Ikrima ne kaha, tumhen mein chand chhoti chhotii baatein na bata dun jinhein ham se Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mashk ke munh se munh laga kar pani peeney ki manaahii ki thi aur (is se bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mana farmaya tha ke) koi shakhs apne padaus ko apni diwar mein khoontii wghaira gaadney se rokey."
5628,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mashk ke munh se pani peeney ki manaahii farma di thi.
5629,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mashk ke munh se pani peeney ko mana farmaya tha.
5630,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab tum mein se koi shakhs pani piey to (peeney ke) bartan main (paanii peetey huey) saans na ley aur jab tum mein se koi shakhs peshab karey to daahiney hath ko zakar (private part) par na pherey aur jab istinja karey to daahiney hath se na kare.
5631,Anas (Raziallahu anhu) 2 ya teen saanson mein pani peetey they.
5632,"Huzefa bin Yamaan (Raziallahu anhu) madaain mein they. unhon-ne pani maanga to aik dehati ne unko chandi ke bartan mein pani la kar diya, unhon-ne bartan ko is par phenk maara phir kaha maine bartan sirf is wjah se phainkaa hai ke us shakhs ko main us se mana kar chuka tha lekin ye baaz na aaya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein resham w deebaa ke pahnney se aur soney aur chandi ke bartan mein khaney peeney se mana kya tha aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne irshad farmaya tha ke ye cheezein un kuffaar ke liye duniya mein hain aur tumhen aakhirat mein milengey."
5633,ham Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath nikley phir unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka zikr kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke soney aur chandi ke piyaale mein na piyaa karo aur na resham w deebaa pehna karo kyonke ye cheezein unke liye duniya mein hain aur tumharey liye aakhirat mein hain.
5634,aur unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo shakhs chandi ke bartan mein koi cheez peetaa hai to wo shakhs apne pet mein dozakh ki aag bhadkaa raha hai.
5635,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein saat (7) chizon ka hukm diya tha aur saat (7) chizon se ham ko mana farmaya tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein bimar ki iyaadat karne, janazey ke peechhey chalney, chheenkney waley ke jawab main ( يرحمك الله ( kahney, dawat karne waley ki dawat ko qabool karne, salam phailaaney, mazloom ki madad karne aur qism khaney ke baad kaffara ada karne ka hukm farmaya tha aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein soney ki angoothiyon se, chandi mein peeney ya (farmaayaa) chandi ke bartan mein peeney se, میثر (zeen ya kajaawa ke uper resham ka gaddaa (ke istemal karne se aur qassi (misr ke aas-paas taiyaar kya janey wala aik kapda jis mein resham ke dhaagey bhi istemal hotey they) ke istemal karne se aur resham w deebaa aur istibraq pahnney se mana farmaya tha."
5636,logon ne Arfa ke din Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke rozey ke mutaalliq shuba kya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein doodh ka aik katora pesh kya gaya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey nosh farmaayaa.
5637,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aik Arab aurat ka zikr kya gaya phir aap ne Usaid Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) ko unke paas unhein laney ke liye kisi ko bhejney ka hukm diya chunanche unhon-ne bheja aur wo aaiin aur banii-Saaida ke qile mein utriin aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi tashrif laey aur unke paas gaey. aap ne dekha ke aik aurat sar jhukaaey baithi hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jab unse guftgu ki to wo kehney lagiin ke main tum se Allah ki panah maangtii hun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke maine tujh ko panah dii! logon ne baad mein unse poochha. tumhen malum bhi hai ye kon they. us aurat ne jawab diya ke nahi. logon ne kaha ke ye to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) they tum se nikah ke liye tashrif laey they. is par wo boliin ke phir to main badi bad-bakht hun (ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko naraz karke wapas kar diyaa) isi din Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey aur Saqeefa bani saaida main apne sahabi ke sath baithey phir farmaya ke Sahal! pani pulaao. maine unke liye ye piyala nikala aur unhein usmein pani pilaayaa. Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey liye bhi wahi piyala nikal kar laey aur ham ne bhi usmein pani piyaa. rawi ne bayan kya ke phir baad mein khaleefa Umar-bin Abdul-Azeez (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne unse ye maang liya tha aur unhon-ne ye unko hiba kar diya tha.
5638,maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka piyala Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas dekha hai wo phat gaya tha to Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey chandi se jod diya. phir Aasim ne bayan kya ke wo umda chaudaa piyala hai. chamakdaar lakdi ka bana hua. bayan kya ke Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya ke maine us piyaale se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bahut baar pilaya hai. rawi ne bayan kya ke Ibne-Sirin ne kaha ke us piyaale mein lohey ka aik halqa tha. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne chaha ke uski jagah chandi ya soney ka halqa judwaa dein lekin abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse kaha ke jisey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne banaya hai is mein hargiz koi tabdili na karo chunanche unhon-ne ye irada chhod diya.
5639,main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath tha aur Asr ki Namaz ka waqt ho gaya thodey se bachey huey pani ke siwa hamarey paas aur koi pani nahi tha usey aik bartan mein rakh kar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein laya gaya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usmein apna hath daala aur apni ungliyan phaila diin phir farmaya aao wuzu kar lo ye Allah ki taraf se barkat hai. maine dekha ke pani Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ungliyon ke darmyan se phoot-phoot kar nikal raha tha chunanche sab logon ne us se wuzu kya aur piyaa bhii. maine uski parwah kiye baghair ke pet mein kitna pani ja raha hai khub pani piyaa kyonke mujhey malum ho gaya tha ke barkat ka pani hai. maine Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha aap log us waqt kitni tadaad mein they? batlaya ke aik hazaar char so. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Amr ne Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se ki hai aur Husain aur Amr-bin-Murra ne Salim se bayan kya aur unse Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke sahaba ki us waqt tadaad pandarah so thi. uski mutabiat (pairavi) Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ne Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se ki hai.
